{
  "id": "adv_card_rui_11_01",
  "title": "天動瑠依 1話 サキュバスってなんですか！？",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 0.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、お疲れ様です\n……それ、何を読んでいるんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}‚ good work today.\n…What is that you’re reading?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、星見プロのアイドルを起用した恋愛ゲーム\n『もし恋』は、瑠依も知ってるだろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ it's about the romance game featuring Hoshimi Pro idols.\nYou know about \"Moshi-Koi‚\" right‚ Rui?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 246.53088249999922,
          "startTime": 6.3666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "その制作会社から、新しい企画が届いたんだけど……\nそうだ。良かったら瑠依の意見も聞かせてくれないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The production company sent over a new proposal…\nRight. If you don't mind‚ could I hear your thoughts?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.9666659673,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9266.6666667,
          "startTime": 26.233332634
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "新しい企画ですか。もちろんです、拝見させて下さい\nえーと……ファンと一緒に作るゲーム？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A new proposal. Of course‚ let me take a look.\nLet's see… A game made together with fans?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.633332634,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "へぇ……ファンの投票でゲームのジャンルやユニット名\nそれに衣装も決めていくんですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh… So the fans vote to decide the genre‚ unit name‚\nand even the costumes.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.133332634,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "ファンの意見がこんなに反映されるなんて……\n凄く、面白い企画だと思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To think the fans' opinions are reflected this much…\nI think it's a very interesting project.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.1333351772,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、俺もいい企画だと思う。この企画が本決まりに\nなったら、瑠依にも出演を相談させてほしい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ I agree. Once this project is officially greenlit‚\nI'd like to talk to you about appearing in it‚ Rui.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.1238008254,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6342.867685100004,
          "startTime": 54.4666685105
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、気が早いですよ。もう少し資料を\n読み込んでみないと……これがゲームのジャンルですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe‚ you're getting ahead of yourself. I need to\nread through the materials more… so this is the genre list.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.3333351772,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "ゲームのテーマ候補は……えーっと、まずは\n『本格？　どたばた！！　サスペンス！？！？』ですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The theme candidates are… Let's see‚ first is\n\"Authentic? Slapstick!! Suspense!?!?\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.7333351772,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "不安や恐怖で、ドキドキするような話ですよね\n誰が演じても、普段とのギャップが出て面白そう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It must be a story that makes the heart race with fear and unease.\nNo matter who plays it‚ the gap from their usual self would be fun.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.4333351772,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3976.4537546000015,
          "startTime": 76.4097889318
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "次は『幼馴染との切なく爽やかなラブストーリー』……\n誰が幼馴染の役でもハマりそうで、楽しみですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Next is \"A Bitter-Sweet and Refreshing Love Story with a Childhood Friend\"…\nAnyone would fit the childhood friend role perfectly. I'm looking forward to it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.4000018438,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "『踊り子達と繰り広げる異世界冒険ファンタジー』や\n『ほろ苦くも厳しい現実に立ち向かうSF』もあるな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There's also \"Another World Adventure Fantasy with Dancers\"\nand \"SF Confronting a Bittersweet and Harsh Reality.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.2666685105,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "この辺りのジャンルはゲームならではだよな\nどんな内容に決まるのか気になるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "These genres are really unique to gaming.\nI'm curious to see what will be chosen.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.9333351772,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2895.8863311000014,
          "startTime": 99.8292215083
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01-rui009.m4a",
      "text": "そして『どきドキ♡ラブコメファンタジー』……\nこれは正直、私にはよく分からないジャンルですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And \"Doki Doki♡ Rom-com Fantasy\"…\nHonestly‚ this is a genre I'm not very familiar with‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.2666685105,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01-rui010.m4a",
      "text": "でも、どれに決まってもきっと面白くなると思います\nところで、配役はどうやって決めるんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "but I'm sure it will be interesting no matter what is picked.\nBy the way‚ how are the roles decided?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.0666685105,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "各ジャンルに、先方がランダムに四人ずつ割り振る\nらしい。役柄は、後でくじで決めようと思ってる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The production company randomly assigns four people to each genre.\nI’m planning to decide the specific roles by drawing lots later.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.4611366932,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01-rui011.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど……それなら配役に意外性が生まれますし\nみんなの新しい一面を引き出せるかもしれませんね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… That would create some unexpected casting‚\nand might bring out a new side of everyone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.1333351772,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01-rui012.m4a",
      "text": "……あの、{user}さん。もし良かったら\nこの企画、私も参加させてもらえませんか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Um‚ {user}. If you don't mind‚\ncould I also participate in this project?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.5333351772,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01-rui013.m4a",
      "text": "こんな風にファンの声に応える方法があったなんて……\n私には思いもよりませんでした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I never imagined there was a way to respond to the fans like this…\nIt never even crossed my mind.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.0047922214,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01-rui014.m4a",
      "text": "それに私も、自分の新しい一面を探してみたいんです\nもっとファンの期待に応えるために、上を目指すために",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Besides‚ I want to find a new side of myself as well.\nTo meet the fans' expectations more‚ and to aim higher.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.409629576,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "……分かった。決めたよ\nこの企画、ぜひやらせてほしいと返事をしよう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Alright. It's settled.\nI'll send a reply saying we definitely want to join this project.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.2666685105,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 160.9670053171
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 160.9670053171
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "（こうして企画がスタートし）\n（瑠依も参加することになったのだが……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（And so the project began‚）\n（and Rui ended up participating…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 163.8000018438,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1366.6666666999845,
          "startTime": 165.1666685105
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 170.0333351772
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01-rui015.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、お疲れ様です\n――今、お時間いいですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}‚ good work today.\n――Do you have a moment right now?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 170.0333351772,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "る、瑠依？　怒ってるようだけど、どうしたんだ？\n……もしかして、例のゲームの件か？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "R-Rui? You look angry‚ what's wrong?\n…Is it about that game project?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 177.1666685105,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 179.9879800486
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01-rui016.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ。テーマが『どきドキ♡ラブコメファンタジー』に\n決まったのは……まぁ、いいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. That the theme was decided as\n\"Doki Doki♡ Rom-com Fantasy\" is… well‚ fine.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 183.3333351772,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 186.1962565112
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01-rui017.m4a",
      "text": "でもなんで、私がサキュバスの役なんですか！\nそもそも、サキュバスってなんですか！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But why am I playing the role of a Succubus!\nFirst of all‚ what even IS a Succubus!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 189.7666685105,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 192.5868645359
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01-rui018.m4a",
      "text": "エ、エッチなやつじゃないんですか！？\nそもそも配役の半数がサキュバスなのもおかしいです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is-Isn't it some kind of lewd character!?\nBesides‚ it's strange that half the cast are Succubi!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 195.3999977749,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 199.4588372875
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01-rui019.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、不満がある訳じゃないんですけど……\nで、でも……っ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ it's not that I'm dissatisfied…\nB-But…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 202.8333311082,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 204.5131454159
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "お、落ち着いてくれ、瑠依。配役は最初に\n宣言した通り、公平にくじ引きで決めただろ？　な？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "C-Calm down‚ Rui. The roles were decided\nfairly by drawing lots‚ just as I declared. Right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 207.5333311082,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01-rui020.m4a",
      "text": "うっ……確かにくじで決まりました……\nくじを引いたのも、私でした……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh… It certainly was decided by lots…\nAnd I was the one who drew the lot…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 215.6999977749,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 218.8325329472
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "配役はサキュバスが多めなのは確かだ\nでも、あまり過激な内容にはならないし、俺がさせない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's true there are a lot of Succubi in the cast.\nBut the content won't be too extreme‚ I won't let that happen.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 222.0188324713,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01-rui021.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんが、そう言うなら……\nいつも私達アイドルのことを、守ってくれていますし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you say so‚ {user}…\nYou've always protected us idols‚ after all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 229.4193936699,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 234.2699930518
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "それに、ゲームのジャンルはファン投票で決まっただろ\nつまり、ファンの気持ちが反映されているんだから――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Besides‚ the genre was decided by fan voting.\nThat means it reflects the fans' wishes――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 237.9763381315,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 241.4366505632
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01-rui022.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんは私の大切なファンの方々が\nエッチな内容を求めているって言いたいんですか！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are you suggesting that my precious fans\nare wishing for lewd content!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 244.8999886196,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 253.3333311082
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "え……あ……投票数を見るとそういうことに……ゴホン\nいや違う、ファンが求めているのは瑠依の新たな一面だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Uh… well… looking at the vote count‚ it seems so… Ahem\nNo‚ that's not it. What the fans want is a new side of you‚ Rui.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 253.3333311082,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "舞台や映画とも違う、『ゲーム』という媒体だからこそ\n瑠依の新しい魅力を引き出せるはずだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because it’s a medium like \"games‚\" which is different from stage or film‚\nwe can definitely bring out your new charm.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 262.2999977749,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 265.2079426457
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01-rui023.m4a",
      "text": "……そ、そうですよね。『もし恋』も、アイドルとの\n恋愛を楽しめる、ゲームならではの要素が好評でしたし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I-I see. \"Moshi-Koi\" was also popular for its unique\ngaming elements that let you enjoy romance with idols.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 269.2999977749,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01-rui024.m4a",
      "text": "ゲームだからこそ、いつもの私とは全然違う\n新しい天動瑠依を表現出来る……そういうことですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because it's a game‚ I can express a new Tenndo Rui\nthat is completely different from my usual self… I see.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 278.9666644415,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 284.2035885503
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01-rui025.m4a",
      "text": "何よりも、ファンのみなさんが私の新たな一面を見たい\nと思って下さっているなら、その期待に応えたいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Above all‚ if the fans want to see a new side of me‚\nI want to live up to those expectations.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 288.6333311082,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、瑠依ならきっと応えられるはずだ\n立派にサキュバスを演じられるよう祈ってるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right‚ I'm sure you can live up to them‚ Rui.\nI'll be praying for you to give a splendid performance as a Succubus.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 296.3666644415,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 299.6625454595
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01-rui026.m4a",
      "text": "うまく丸め込まれた気もしますけど、納得は出来ました\nまだ自信はありませんけど……頑張ってみます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I feel like I've been sweet-talked into it‚ but I'm convinced.\nI'm still not confident… but I'll do my best.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 304.6666644415,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
